BILLABLE_ROUTES=/api/v1/documents,/api/v1/cases,/api/v1/clients,/api/v1/forms,/api/v1/ai,/api/v1/search

# X-Request-ID behavior:
# - If X-Request-ID header is present, it will be used for idempotency
# - If missing, a UUID will be automatically generated
# - Each request_id ensures exactly one UsageEvent is created (deduplication)
# - Usage events include UTC timestamps and tenant/user context from auth middleware
